  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nWhen a test fails, it would be great if, in addition to what kind of failure (revert, expectation failed, etc.), it would also spit out the line/column in the test file that it failed on. This would match the norms in other testing suites I've used. I can read the trace in `-vvv` to get this but it's not as intuitive/quick.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
